    "doc_template": {
      "path": "templates/doc_module.md",
      "description": "Template enriquecido para documentación de módulos",
      "content": "# {{module}}\n\n> **Status:** {{status}} | **Version:** {{version}} | **Owner:** {{owner}}\n\n## 📌 Responsabilidad\n\n{{responsibility}}\n\n## 🎯 Use Cases\n\n{{use_cases}}\n\n## 🔗 Interfaces\n\n### Inputs\n```json\n{{input_schema}}\n```\n\n### Outputs\n```json\n{{output_schema}}\n```\n\n### Events Published\n- `{{module}}.{{event_name}}`: {{event_description}}\n\n### Events Consumed\n- `{{dependency}}.{{event_name}}`: {{event_description}}\n\n## 💻 Code Examples\n\n### Python\n```python\n{{python_example}}\n```\n\n### JavaScript\n```javascript\n{{javascript_example}}\n```\n\n### cURL\n```bash\n{{curl_example}}\n```\n\n## 🔒 Seguridad\n\n- **Scopes requeridos:** {{scopes}}\n- **Rate limiting:** {{rate_limit}}\n- **Secrets utilizados:** {{secrets}} (gestionados por vault)\n- **Sanitization:** {{sanitization_notes}}\n\n## 🧪 Tests\n\n- **Coverage:** {{coverage_pct}}%\n- **Unit tests:** {{unit_test_count}}\n- **Integration tests:** {{integration_test_count}}\n- **Contract tests:** {{contract_test_count}}\n\n### Ejecutar tests\n```bash\n{{test_command}}\n```\n\n## 📊 Métricas y SLOs\n\n- **Latency p95:** {{latency_p95}}ms (target: ≤200ms)\n- **Error rate:** {{error_rate}}% (target: ≤1%)\n- **Availability:** {{availability}}% (target: ≥99.9%)\n\n## 🚨 Troubleshooting\n\n### Error: {{common_error_1}}\n**Causa:** {{error_cause_1}}\n**Solución:** {{error_solution_1}}\n\n### Error: {{common_error_2}}\n**Causa:** {{error_cause_2}}\n**Solución:** {{error_solution_2}}\n\n## 🔗 Módulos Relacionados\n\n- [{{related_module_1}}]({{related_module_1_path}}): {{relationship_1}}\n- [{{related_module_2}}]({{related_module_2_path}}): {{relationship_2}}\n\n## ⚡ Performance Tips\n\n- {{performance_tip_1}}\n- {{performance_tip_2}}\n- {{performance_tip_3}}\n\n## 🔄 Changelog\n\nVer [CHANGELOG.md](./CHANGELOG.md) para historial completo.\n\n## 📅 Última actualización\n\n{{last_update}} por {{last_author}}\n\n---\n\n📚 [Documentation Index](../../index.json) | 🏗️ [Architecture](../../architecture/) | 🐛 [Report Issue]({{issue_tracker_url}})\n"
    },
    "docs_changelog": {
      "path": "docs/v1/CHANGELOG.md",
      "description": "Changelog con diff visualization y semantic versioning",
      "schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "version": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "changes": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "type": { "type": "string", "enum": ["added", "changed", "deprecated", "removed", "fixed", "security"] },
                "module": { "type": "string" },
                "description": { "type": "string" },
                "breaking": { "type": "boolean" },
                "diff_path": { "type": "string" }
              },
              "required": ["type", "description"],
              "additionalProperties": false
            }
          }
        },
        "required": ["version", "date", "changes"],
        "additionalProperties": false
      },
      "example": {
        "version": "1.1.0",
        "date": "2025-10-04",
        "changes": [
          {
            "type": "added",
            "module": "chat_orchestrator",
            "description": "Añadido módulo chat_orchestrator con selección automática de provider",
            "breaking": false
          },
          {
            "type": "changed",
            "module": "auth",
            "description": "Actualizado flujo de autenticación para soportar OAuth 2.1",
            "breaking": true,
            "diff_path": "/docs/v1/diffs/auth_oauth_upgrade.diff"
          },
          {
            "type": "fixed",
            "module": "documentation",
            "description": "Corregidos 8 enlaces rotos en API documentation",
            "breaking": false
          },
          {
            "type": "security",
            "module": "secrets_vault",
            "description": "Actualizado encryption algorithm a AES-256-GCM",
            "breaking": false
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "docs_structure": {
      "tree": [
        "docs/v1/",
        "docs/v1/index.json",
        "docs/v1/modules/<module>/README.md",
        "docs/v1/modules/<module>/CHANGELOG.md",
        "docs/v1/api/*.md",
        "docs/v1/guides/*.md",
        "docs/v1/architecture/*.{mmd,svg}",
        "docs/v1/policies/*.md",
        "docs/v1/reports/*.json",
        "docs/v1/roadmap.md",
        "docs/v1/onboarding.md",
        "docs/v1/troubleshooting/*.md",
        "docs/v1/search_index.json",
        "docs/v1/broken_links_report.json",
        "docs/v1/doc_metrics.json",
        "docs/v1/CHANGELOG.md"
      ]
    }
  },
